OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted1;

""SET NOCOUNT ON;
DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p0;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DECLARE @inserted1 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [ProductImages] USING (
VALUES (@p1, @p2, @p3, 0),
(@p4, @p5, @p6, 1),
(@p7, @p8, @p9, 2),
(@p10, @p11, @p12, 3),
(@p13, @p14, @p15, 4),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, 5),
(@p19, @p20, @p21, 6),
(@p22, @p23, @p24, 7),
(@p25, @p26, @p27, 8),
(@p28, @p29, @p30, 9),
(@p31, @p32, @p33, 10)) AS i ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId])
VALUES (i.[Caption], i.[Path], i.[ProductId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted1;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [ProductImages] t
INNER JOIN @inserted1 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];" (0723d8ff)
